{"tid":1332100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場","createTime":"2019-07-19T07:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T01:51:30.000Z","uid":238051,"like":480,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"f9ef9612d5512e81d43ff33878d950780e3804a2","tid":1332100,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:35:48.000Z","msg":"由6.12開始，冇委任證自稱警員嘅情況日益嚴重<br />\n市民 - 甚至警方本身 - 都未能辨識呢啲是否真．警察<br />\n個多月以來政府都未有辦法解決嚴重嘅問題<br />\n所以黎緊相信要用民間智慧去解決<br />\n<br />\n唔好誤會，呢個post未必可以解決到整個問題<br />\n只希望踏出第一步，慢慢令社會見到問題嚴重性及普及性<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mkorzkv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmkorzkv.png&h=53d4ac3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面對上圖的無證騎士<br />\n我地要一齊履行良好市民嘅責任<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">清楚指出懷疑冒警行為！</span></strong></span><br />\n記住，冒警（竟然）不是嚴重罪行<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>留意不要自行逮捕冒警人士</strong></span></span><br />\n有需要時可以要求附近有委任證的警員幫忙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4UKk7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4UKk7e.png&h=836b7bbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面對懷疑持有攻擊性武器的冒警人士<br />\n我地的確有權行駛<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公民逮捕權</span><br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">極不建議自行逮捕</span></strong></span>！<br />\n因為呢類人士通常會聯群結隊，而且嗜血成狂<br />\n但如果情非得已必須進行逮捕<br />\n必定要提出<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>懷疑冒警根據（未能出示委任證）</strong></span></span><br />\n及逮捕原因<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（藏有攻擊性武器/傷害他人身體）</strong></span></span><br />\n更要聲明正<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>行使公民逮捕權</strong></span></span><br />\n咁先可以在法律前先保障自己及協助你進行逮捕的市民<br />\n但記住我地極不建議自行逮捕疑犯！<br />\n<br />\n記住，即使你唔自行進行逮捕<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>幫口嗌出聲及指證懷疑犯罪行為都有非常重要嘅作用！</strong></span></span><br />\n任何良好市民任何時候都有責任指出懷疑犯罪行為<br />\n千祈唔好因為怕事而收聲<br />\n咁只會助長真正犯罪嘅人繼續做壞事！<br />\n<br />\n希望手足們喺呢個post練習如何處理以上情境<br />\n試下講下：<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre><br />\n亦都試下幫手喺其他post宣揚出去<br />\n令更多人正視香港冒警的嚴重問題！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第一步希望記者們可以留意到！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以下為可能有用連結：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n你涉嫌冒警及嚴重傷害他人身體，我而家要行使《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101條第2項將你拘捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317207</a></span>"},{"pid":"d337e8de19ca339f9d5590f29b8dcef9bae406e2","tid":1332100,"uid":238051,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"110255c98654a7068083b362ff8a4f93a775d6b2","tid":1332100,"uid":258703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d337e8de19ca339f9d5590f29b8dcef9bae406e2","tid":1332100,"uid":238051,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb788e7221680e435e1ba21ba0015e1a8f266b6","tid":1332100,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:44:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bcab35ad8584dc3f29fd55fb48866607a75db17","tid":1332100,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:45:01.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-t